(3, 'CORE 1. Communication and patient participation', '<h1 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin: 12px 0px 20px; font-weight: 700; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-6); color: rgb(35, 91, 168); font-size: 1.5rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;\">Policy</strong></h1><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Communication with patients, their family and carers must be timely, provide information appropriate to their needs, and enable them to make informed decisions regarding their healthcare. Communication, either written or verbal and if needed using an interpreter service, is provided throughout the patient journey - before, during and after consultations.</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-s