(5, 'Annual Leave arrangements', '<h1 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin: 12px 0px 20px; font-weight: 700; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-6); color: rgb(35, 91, 168); font-size: 1.5rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\">Policy</h1><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Saint Luke\'s Medical Centre encourages employees to have an appropriate work-life balance and for permanent employees to take their annual leave entitlement in the year in which that entitlement accrues to ensure appropriate rest and relaxation.</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>This policy aims to ensure that the Practice is able to meet workplace resourcing needs and give each permanent employee the opportunity to take annual leave, at a time which is mutually convenient to both the Practice and the employee, while continuing to offer high-quality services to the Practice’s patients.</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Subject to the terms of any applicable industrial instrument (including an applicable modern award or enterprise agreement), permanent employees (other than shift-workers) are entitled to four or five weeks of paid annual leave for each completed year of service with the Practice according to the applicable award and the National Employment Standards. An employee’s entitlement to annual leave accrues progressively during each year of service and accumulates from year to year.</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Casual employees may request time in where they are unavailable to attend work but are not entitled to paid annual leave.</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Requests for leave from Associate contracted GPs must also adhere to the requirements of the policy and procedure out of mutual respect toward the Practice.</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin: 4px 0px 12px; font-weight: 700; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-4); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 1.125rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Procedure</h3><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>An employee may take annual leave if the employee has a sufficient accrued annual leave entitlement and the employee’s manager approves the taking of leave. An employee who wishes to take annual leave must submit a leave application form to their manager. An employee’s annual leave application form should be submitted to their manager at least three weeks in advance of the proposed commencement of the employee’s period of annual leave. Applications for annual leave given without three (3) weeks notice will require special permission from the appropriate rostering manager prior to submitting the leave form.</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>If the employee does not have the appropriate annual leave accrued by the time annual leave is taken, a written request may be addressed to the Practice Manager to have annual leave be place into negatives to cover the period of leave. Should the Practice Manager agree to this arrangement, both the Practice Manager and the employee will need to sign the written request. The employee then owes a debt to the Practice, and much replenish the negative leave into positives before taking further leave.</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Casual employees, as a courtesy, are still required to submit leave forms for periods of unavailability.</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>&nbsp;</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>&nbsp;</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>This policy does not form part of any contract between the Practice and an employee and is not, and is not intended to be, contractual in nature.</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>The Practice may amend, replace or withdraw this policy at any time.</p>', 1, 0, '', '2024-09-18 10:03:52'),
(6, 'CORE 2. Rights and needs of patients', '<p><span style=\'color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\' id=\"isPasted\">Our practice promotes the value of a strong therapeutic relationship, a relationship based on mutual respect and responsibility for patient health, we respect the rights and needs of patients.</span></p>', 3, 0, '', '2024-09-18 14:04:10'),
(7, 'Planning and Goal Setting C3.1A & B', '<h1 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin: 12px 0px 20px; font-weight: 700; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-6); color: rgb(0, 85, 162); font-size: 1.5rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\">Policy</h1><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Our practice understands that quality clinical care needs to be supported by effective business management. &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Our approach to planning, setting and evaluating goals includes having:</span></p><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 30px !important; list-style-type: disc !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Corporate statements (<a href=\"https://pnp.practicehub.org/policy-and-procedure/edit/20108\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; color: var(--ph-text-color-link); text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\">mission and philosophy&nbsp;</a>and &nbsp;<a href=\"https://pnp.practicehub.org/policy-and-procedure/edit/20243\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; color: var(--ph-text-color-link); text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\">code of conduct)</a></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">A strategic plan</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">An annual business plan</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Defined measures of our performance</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Involving all the team in the plan development and implementation</span></li></ul><h1 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin: 12px 0px 20px; font-weight: 700; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-6); color: rgb(0, 85, 162); font-size: 1.5rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Procedure</h1><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">The leadership team develops a plan annually and reviews this plan quarterly.</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;\">Helpful Resources in PracticeHub Resource Library</strong>:</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;\">Practice management and development</strong></span></p><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 30px !important; list-style-type: disc !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">SWOT Analysis:&nbsp;This enables us to look at our practice and ourselves, and identify: our performance and opportunities for improvement.</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Goal writing tool&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Force Field Analysis: This tool means we can take a goal and identify the driving forces and the restraining forces.</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">One Page Plan</span></li></ul><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;\">Additional External Resources:</strong></span></p><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 30px !important; list-style-type: disc !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.business.gov.au/planning/templates-and-tools/business-plan-template-and-guide\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; color: var(--ph-text-color-link); text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\">Business.gov.au</a></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.nab.com.au/business/moments/manage/planning/business-plan-template\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; color: var(--ph-text-color-link); text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\">NAB</a></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.anz.com.au/business/calculators/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; color: var(--ph-text-color-link); text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\">ANZ – Business Planning</a></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.thebalancesmb.com/one-page-business-plan-templates-4135972\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; color: var(--ph-text-color-link); text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\">The balance small business</a> – see One-page business plan for a service business</span></li></ul>', 4, 0, '', '2024-09-18 14:05:26');
