(9, 'Use of Closed Circuit TV (CCTV) in Practice', '<h1 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin: 12px 0px 20px; font-weight: 700; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-6); color: rgb(0, 85, 162); font-size: 1.5rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\">Policy</h1><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">To assist in providing a safe physical environment, a closed circuit television (CCTV) surveillance system has been installed in the practice. The area covered includes the [e.g. reception desk, waiting area, and hallways].</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none;\">This policy does not relate to the recording of audio. Refer to the appropriate legislation for recordings with audio.</em></span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;\">The practice should balance improvements in safety and security for staff and patients with the need to respect the privacy and confidentiality of medical consultations. The practice also considers where CCTV surveillance is placed within the practice.</strong></span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;\">Objectives of camera surveillance</strong></span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">In the security context, camera surveillance is generally used to achieve the following objectives:</span></p><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 30px !important; list-style-type: disc !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">To deter security incidents e.g. theft, vandalism, violence etc.</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">To gather information that may be used in evidence if a crime is committed within view of the camera (assuming the camera is recording)</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">To allow a security incident to be viewed as it is occurring and an appropriate response to be taken.</span></li></ul><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Key requirements of a CCTV policy and procedure:</span></p><ol style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 5px 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Notification of use of CCTV to patients and staff</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 5px 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Monitoring of the surveillance</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 5px 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Secure storage, retention and destruction or de-identification of footage</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 5px 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Use and disclosure of surveillance records</span></li></ol><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;\">1. Notification of use of CCTV to patients and staff</strong></span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">CCTV cameras should be clearly visible to people in the area that is under surveillance whilst still respecting privacy issues.</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Employees are notified that the cameras are used. New starters should be advised prior to commencing work. The notification includes the kind of surveillance, how it will be carried out, when it will start, whether it will be continuous or intermittent and whether it will be for a specified limited period or ongoing. In the ACT, workers who will “regularly and ordinarily be the subject of the surveillance” must be notified.</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Signs notifying people that they may be under camera surveillance are clearly visible at each entrance to the area under .</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(128, 0, 128);\">OPTIONAL In addition, the practice notifies patients in the patient registration form and in the practice privacy policy that the practice uses CCTV surveillance.</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">The practice has procedures to ensure that patients and others attending the practice with disabilities, language or literacy issues can be notified that the practice uses CCTV surveillance.</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;\">2. Monitoring of the surveillance [SELECT APPLICABLE OPTION]</strong></span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;\">OPTION 1 - Non Continuous Monitoring:</strong></span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">The CCTV is continuously recorded with archived images stored for up to 30 days.</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Regular review of the effectiveness of the above strategies is undertaken to ensure risk and liability are being appropriately managed in a way that maintains the security of staff and others.</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;\">OPTION 2 - Continuous Monitoring: (Not used)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none;\"></strong></span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">In the situations listed above, the camera will only achieve its objectives if it is being continuously monitored or being managed in a way that ensures an appropriate response is activated in the event of a violent incident.</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">The practice has adopted a strategy of continuous monitoring via a control panel and will ensure that employees involved in these surveillance activities are appropriately licensed and trained, as required by security industry legislation.</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;\">3. Secure storage, retention and destruction or de-identification of footage</strong></span></p><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 30px !important; list-style-type: disc !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Use of CCTV equipment should be restricted to authorised employees and contractors only, in accordance with standard operating procedures</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Employees and contractors must seek approval from the practice manager to view any images or footage</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Measures should be taken to protect recorded material against unauthorised access, alteration, dissemination, disclosure, loss or destruction</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Equipment should be maintained to ensure its effective operation</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Relevant recordkeeping practices should be applied</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Information gathered through CCTV and must be kept securely, only for as long as necessary to fulfil the purpose of the cameras and destroyed or de-identified when it is no longer .</span></li></ul><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;\">4. Use and disclosure of surveillance records&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Any record made as a result of surveillance is not be used within the practice or disclosed outside the practice unless the use or disclosure is:</span></p><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 30px !important; list-style-type: disc !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Required by a court order e.g. a subpoena or warrant</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">For a legitimate purpose related to the employment of staff or the legitimate business activities of the practice.</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">To a member or officer of a law enforcement agency (e.g. Police) for use in connection with the detection, investigation or prosecution of an offence.</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">For a purpose that is directly or indirectly related to civil or criminal proceedings.</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; list-style-type: disc !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">Reasonably believed to be necessary to avert an imminent threat of serious violence or of substantial damage to property.</span></li></ul><h1 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin: 12px 0px 20px; font-weight: 700; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-6); color: rgb(0, 85, 162); font-size: 1.5rem; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Procedure</h1><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 12pt;\">The practice will assess requests for access to surveillance records on a case by case basis.</span></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: var(--ph-size-base); margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: \"Source Sans 3\", sans-serif; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: var(--ph-font-lineheight-3); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; lette